Enum Class FlurryEvent

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<FlurryEvent>
com.flurry.android.FlurryEvent
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<FlurryEvent>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum FlurryEvent extends Enum<FlurryEvent>
The FlurryEvent defines the supported types of Flurry standard events, and their predefined parameters.
